  %p<> We haven't worked out the characters completely yet though! But so far, we're thinking about having 4 really cool demo programing guyz as the heroes!!
  %p<> We've also done a really supey-dupey <strong>logo</strong>!!! See how <strong>Jackson Pollock</strong> did it <a href="logo.html">here</a>!!!
