  %p<> We want this to be the best "net" comedy script ever, so we're looking for loadsa <strong>suggestions</strong>!! If you <strong><a href="mailto:oldfart_sd@yahoo.com">mail us</a></strong> with suggestions, we'll <strong>credit</strong> you on these very pages!!! 
  %p<> Remember, the more bizarre and unlikely- the better!! And we really want it to end with an absolutely ridiculous "Cluedo" style ending as well. The CGI server on this site is now <strong>working again</strong>, so we're busy coding the <strong>message board</strong> so we can have some <strong>script conferences</strong>!!!!
